<section class="section">
  <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <span>/</span>
    <span>About</span>
  </nav>

  <div class="about-split">
    <div>
      <h1>About This Site</h1>

      <p class="prose-width">
        Exonumist is a collector-focused reference site built around cataloged New York City
        transportation tokens while also documenting unlisted material, patterns, oddities, errors,
        counterfeits, and related pieces that deserve long-term visibility.
      </p>
    </div>

    <aside class="about-aside">
      <h3>Site Focus</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>NYC transit tokens</li>
        <li>Unlisted, Errors & Oddities</li>
        <li>Collector research</li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="about-split">
    <div>
      <h2>My Collection</h2>

      <p class="prose-width">
        While this site currently focuses on New York City transportation exonumia, my broader collection
        includes Arcade, Hard Times, Civil War, Merchant, and Miscellaneous tokens — basically, interesting
        shiny metal things with history behind them.
      </p>

      <p class="prose-width">
        Listed transportation material follows the Atwood-Coffee Catalogue where applicable. Unlisted items
        are included when they help document discoveries, varieties, errors, oddities, or related collecting
        areas.
      </p>
    </div>

    <aside class="about-aside">
      <h3>Also Collecting</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Civil War tokens</li>
        <li>Hard Times tokens</li>
        <li>Merchant tokens</li>
        <li>Arcade tokens</li>
        <li>Miscellaneous exonumia</li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h2>Want List</h2>

  <p class="section-intro">
    Looking for specific items I am actively seeking? Visit the
    <a href="/wanted/">Want List</a>.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h2>Research & References</h2>

  <p class="section-intro">
    References and organizations useful for transportation token research and catalog information.
  </p>

  <div class="grid-narrow">
    {% for resource in resources | sort(attribute="order") %}
      {% if resource.pub != false %}
        <a class="card-link" href="{{ resource.urlRef | resolveUrlRef(site) }}">
          <article class="resource-card resource-card-with-media">
            <div class="resource-card-body">
              <strong>{{ resource.title }}</strong>
              <p>{{ resource.text }}</p>
            </div>

            {% if resource.image %}
              <div class="resource-card-media">
                <img
                  class="resource-card-logo"
                  src="{{ resource.image }}"
                  alt="{{ resource.title }}" />
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          </article>
        </a>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
